Package: shapley
Type: Package
Title: Shapley Values for Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-12
Authors@R: person(
    "Dan", "Yavorsky",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    email = "dyavorsky@gmail.com"
    )
Description: Computes Shapley/LMG variable importance values by averaging each
    predictor's marginal R-squared contribution over all possible orderings.
    Supports continuous outcomes (linear regression, R-squared), binary outcomes
    (logistic regression, McFadden pseudo-R-squared), and ordinal outcomes
    (proportional odds regression, McFadden pseudo-R-squared). Control variables
    can be specified and are held fixed across all subset models, so Shapley
    values attribute only the incremental fit above the controls.
